e handkerchief and put it in my pocket.', '我折好手绢，放进口袋里。'), (4976, 'The paper should be folded in half.', '这张纸应该对折。'), (4977, 'The border guard folded his arms across his chest and glared the front.', '边防战士双手交叉于胸前紧紧瞪着前方。'), (4978, 'A lot of folks are upset at the changes.', '许多人对这些变化感到不安。'), (4979, 'This is no place for young folk.', '这可不是年轻人该去的地方。'), (4980, 'The town folk know him as Mr. Dickey.', '镇上的人们都知道他是迪基先生。'), (4981, 'I\'d like you to meet my folks.', '我想要你见见我的父母。'), (4982, 'He is a very popular folk singer.', '他是一位很受欢迎的民歌手。'), (4983, 'The little boy followed his father out.', '小男孩跟随他父亲出去了。'), (4984, 'They blew up the bridge so that the enemy couldn\'t follow them.,', '们炸毁了桥梁,使敌人无法追赶他们。'), (4985, 'If you ignore your diet, trouble will follow..', '果你忽视自己的饮食，必然会遇到麻烦.'), (4986, 'He followed every word of the trial.', '他注意听着裁判的每句话。'), (4987, 'If you want to complain, you\'d better follow the correct procedure.,', '果你要投诉,最好遵循正确的程序。'), (4988, 'Follow this road until you get to the corner, then turn left.,', '着这条路走到拐角处,然后向左转。'), (4989, 'I didn\'t quite follow; could you explain it again?', '我不太明白，你能再解释一下吗？'), (4990, 'The following item is a piano solo by Jackson.', '下一个节目是杰克逊表演的钢琴独奏。'), (4991, 'It rained on the day we arrived, but the following day was sunny.', '我们到达的那天正下雨，但次日天气晴朗。'), (4992, 'Please choose from the following three selections.', '请从下列的三个选择中选择。'), (4993, 'A fond mother may spoil her child.', '溺爱的母亲可能会宠坏她的孩子。'), (4994, 'The fond father smiled with pleasure.', '溺爱孩子的父亲高兴地微笑了。'), (4995, 'I am not fond of solitude.', '我不喜欢孤独。'), (4996, 'He was fond of drawing when he was a child.', '他还是个孩子时就喜欢画画。'), (4997, 'He is fond of high-sounding phrases.', '他爱用夸大的词句。'), (4998, 'She has many shortcomings, but we\'re all very fond of her.', '虽然她有许多缺点，但我们都很喜欢她。'), (4999, 'My little son is fond of playing practical jokes on me.', '我的小儿子喜欢对我玩恶作剧。'), (5000, 'He has a fond belief in his own cleverness.', '他盲目相信自己的聪明。'), (5001, 'Her father is extremely rich; many fond hopes