ilure of the electricity supplies, the city was in chaos.,', '力供应中断,城市陷于混乱之中。'), (15150, 'Without rules, people would live in a state of chaos.,', '无规则,人们将在混乱状态中生活。'), (15151, 'Chaos often breeds life, when order breeds habit.', '混沌常常孕育着生命，而秩序会产生习惯。'), (15152, 'The Chaos gods demand their souls.', '混沌邪神需要他们的灵魂。'), (15153, 'The novelist characterizes his heroine as capricious and passionate.', '这位小说家把女主人公刻画成变化无常而又多情的人。'), (15154, 'He may be characterized as a man of hobbies.', '他可以被称作是一个有癖好的人。'), (15155, 'Your work is characterized by lack of attention to details.', '你的工作特点是缺乏对细节的注意。'), (15156, 'True charity doesn\'t consist in almsgiving.', '真正的慈善不在于施舍。'), (15157, 'This charity is a nonprofit organization.', '这个慈善团体是个非盈利性组织。'), (15158, 'The priest preached a sermon on the need of charity.', '牧师在布道会上宣讲慈爱的必要。'), (15159, 'Her charm rests in her happy smile.', '她的魅力在于她幸福的微笑。'), (15160, 'The use of dialect lent great charm to the work ', '方言的运用给这部作品增添了巨大的魅力。'), (15161, 'The hotel is full of charm and character.', '这家旅馆风格独特，极具吸引力。'), (15162, 'Her charm prejudiced the judges in her favour.', '她姿色迷人，因而评委都偏向她。'), (15163, 'The Irish are known for their charm and vivacity, as well as for the beauty of the Irish girls.', '爱尔兰人以其魅力和活泼而著称，爱尔兰姑娘的美貌也声名远扬。'), (15164, 'Leung\'s relaxed charm and matinee-idol looks make it easy to overlook the complexity of his performances.', '梁朝伟那轻松的迷人魅力与电影偶像的美貌使他对复杂角色的刻画得心应手。'), (15165, 'You should read the Charter of the United Nations.', '你应该阅读一下联合国宪章。'), (15166, 'The rights of our citizens are governed by charter.', '我们公民的权利是由宪章规定的。'), (15167, 'The company was granted a charter trade in the occupied territory.', '这家公司被授予特权，可以在被占领地区进行贸易活动。'), (15168, 'He came round last week and we chatted for a while.,', '星期他顺道来访,我们闲谈了一会。'), (15169, 'He likes to chat with his e-pals on the Internet.', '他喜欢上网与网友聊天。'), (15170, 'Life is hope, so we should cherish life..', '命就是希望.'), (15171, 'I cherish my independence.', '我很珍惜我的自由。'), (15172, 'I cherish the memory o