rsistent pursuer of truth.', '他是个坚持不懈追求真理的人。'), (18061, 'His great success cannot depart from his persistent effort.', '他取得这么大的成功和他坚持不懈的努力分不开。'), (18062, 'A persistent cough may be a symptom of tuberculosis.', '持续的咳嗽可能是肺病的症候。'), (18063, 'His persistent questions finally goaded me into an angry reply.', '他三番五次地问问题惹得我回答时也没有好气。'), (18064, 'Stores of grain are frequently attacked by pests.', '储存的谷物经常受到害虫的破坏。'), (18065, 'It won\'t be long before we can be rid of the pest altogether.', '不要太久，我们就能把这种害虫消除干净。'), (18066, 'That child is being a real pest.', '那个孩子真讨厌。'), (18067, 'My little brother is a pest when he spoils my games.', '我的小弟弟破坏我的各种游戏真讨厌。'), (18068, 'Many subscribers\' names are in the petition.', '请愿书上有很多签名者的名字。'), (18069, 'They signed a petition in support of the workers\' demands.', '他们在请愿书上签名，支持工人的请求。'), (18070, 'She made a silent petition to God for help.', '她默默地祈求上帝给予帮助。'), (18071, 'She filed a petition for divorce.', '她提出了离婚申请。'), (18072, 'They rejected his petition for naturalization.', '他们拒绝了他的入籍申请。'), (18073, 'The paymasters of these petty crooks are the big crime syndicates.', '操纵这帮小流氓的就是那个大犯罪集团。'), (18074, 'In his short life he had run the entire gamut of crime, from petty theft to murder.,,', '短短的一生中,从小偷小摸到杀人,什么罪都犯过。'), (18075, 'Don\'t bug me with petty details.', '不要讲那些琐碎的细节来烦我。'), (18076, 'People do not discourage this kind of petty work.', '人们对这种次要的工作不加以阻止。'), (18077, 'She grew tired of his petty jealousies.', '她越来越讨厌他那种心胸狭窄的忌妒行为。'), (18078, 'She is very petty at times.', '她有时很小心眼。'), (18079, 'The physiological needs are reasonably satisfied.', '生理的需要得到合理的满足。'), (18080, 'Objective To Study the effect of Haematococcus pluvialis powder on physiological metabolism of Wistar rats.', '目的观察红球藻粉对大鼠生理的影响。'), (18081, 'Certain species of aquatic animals are capable of producing physiological shocks.', '某些种类的水生生物能够引起生理学的电击。'), (18082, 'From a physiological standpoint \"health\"refers to a persons quality of health and their ability to adapt to the outer world